1. The collaborative style of influencing is:
Solution : B. Appropriate when buy-in from the other team is critical

2. The assertive style of influencing is:
Solution : C. Best when quick, decisive action needs to be taken

3. Effective ways to influence others include:
Solution : D. All of the above

4. The inspiring style of influencing:
Solution : A. Is used when the other person responds well to charisma, enthusiasm, and emotion
